name: Magic Cup
description: Only one who watches attentively will hear what the cup has to say, make sure you stay long enough... * Finally... You made it here. It's warm and it smells comforting, like something you felt you always knew but can't quite describe. Maybe you can sit here and stay for a while...* Add the Magic Cup to your wallet to be able to always have it on the go. It's easy to access, take it out of your pocket and it will suck you right back in. Digital pixel artwork made in 2021.
